      <div class="block__section">
        <p>By donating to the Big Change Fund you are supporting people who are homeless with the practical items they need to build new lives off the streets.</p>
        <p>This central fund brings together charities, organisations and people who want to end homelessness to use donations in the most effective way to support change.</p>
        <p>If everyone who lives, works or visits Manchester donates, together we can make a Big Change in our city!</p>
